AR-005\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:13 AR-006\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:27 AR-007\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:53 AR-008\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:16 AR-009\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:41 AR-010\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:10 AR-011\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:30 AR-012\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:39 AR-013\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 05:39 AR-014\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 05:59 AR-015\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 06:18 AR-016\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 06:49 AR-017\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 06:53 AR-018\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:26 AR-019\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:45 AR-020\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 08:12 AR-021\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 08:42 AR-022\n","exit":0,"description":"List existing AR directories","truncated":false},"title":"List existing AR directories","time":{"start":1775869020732,"end":1775869020748}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775869020759,"sessionID":"ses_285f58013ffeKww2tcSyTI77S4","part":{"id":"prt_d7a0ac91a0015mgzra57Q6bInB","messageID":"msg_d7a0ab617001IwB8yoZjPSkAJK","sessionID":"ses_285f58013ffeKww2tcSyTI77S4","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-2f7dd611c97047008d1366e9aaaeacf2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries) Implementation Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module**: `cmd`\n4: **Language**: Go\n5: **Size**: M\n6: **Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n7: \n8: ## Task Breakdown\n9: \n10: ### Task 1: Verify cmd/agentd directory structure and implementation\n11: - [ ] Verify cmd/agentd directory exists\n12: - [ ] Verify main.go exists\n13: - [ ] Verify main.go implements controller-runtime manager initialization\n14: - [ ] Verify metrics-bind-address flag is defined (default: \":8080\")\n15: - [ ] Verify health-probe-bind-address flag is defined (default: \":8081\")\n16: - [ ] Verify leader-elect flag is defined (default: false)\n17: - [ ] Verify zap logger is initialized\n18: - [ ] Verify manager is created with proper options\n19: - [ ] Verify reconciler is registered with manager\n20: - [ ] Verify health checks are registered (/healthz, /readyz)\n21: - [ ] Verify signal handlers are configured (SIGINT, SIGTERM)\n22: \n23: **Verification**: Run `go build ./cmd/agentd` and verify binary compiles successfully\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ### Task 2: Verify cmd/picod directory structure and implementation\n28: - [ ] Verify cmd/picod directory exists\n29: - [ ] Verify main.go exists\n30: - [ ] Verify flags.go exists\n31: - [ ] Verify main.go implements HTTP server initialization\n32: - [ ] Verify --port flag is defined (defa